{"tid":2355972,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓空姐跨年Staycation陳屍酒店浴缸　12男涉姦殺　9人仍在逃","createTime":"2021-01-06T12:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T07:32:30.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f00e1515a1abd40869b220c97160454ce5bceac","tid":2355972,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"菲律賓航空旗下菲航快運（PAL Express）一名23歲空姐達塞拉（Christine Angelica Dacera）元旦中午被發現陳屍在馬尼拉都會區馬卡蒂市（Makati）城市花園大酒店（City Garden Grand Hotel）的旅館房間浴缸内。前一晚她與同事及一些不認識的人一起在該酒店開除夕派對。警方初步檢驗指死因為主動脈瘤破裂，但生前疑遭性侵，有12名男性涉嫌強姦及殺人被落案檢控，目前只有３人被捕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423310890541387776576498.png/OVX-eseR-11NEuVd4iu_FvSdAug6dHM3dOLwC3Ti8As?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423310890541387776576498.png%2FOVX-eseR-11NEuVd4iu_FvSdAug6dHM3dOLwC3Ti8As%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=60e571cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23歲的達塞拉（Dacera）元旦中午被發現在酒店房間的浴缸中昏迷（<a href=\"http://圖取自instagram.com/xtinedacera\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAinstagram.com%2Fxtinedacera&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=16603936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自instagram.com/xtinedacera</a>）<br />\n<br />\n23歲的達塞拉（Dacera）於2021年1月1日中午被發現在酒店房間的浴缸中昏迷，朋友和酒店員工曾替她做心肺復甦無效，送醫後宣佈不治。<br />\n<br />\n馬尼拉《新海峽時報》5日引述該市警察局局長Depositar說，儘管最初從動脈瘤爆裂推斷達塞拉死與自然，但顯然有一些其他因素促成，達塞拉的生殖器有撕裂和精液，手臂和腿上也有瘀傷，挫傷和划痕。星期一（4日）向檢方提出強姦及殺人罪的臨時指控，針對多名在她死前一同入住該酒店兩個相鄰房間的人，Depositar補充說：「他們中只有三個是達塞拉的朋友。其他人對她來說是陌生人。」目前檢方仍在等待詳細屍檢結果和毒理學報告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423310888255361024290613.png/YJqlIMOF3zH_0xkHu4fb5xExTC-e0myyuQsjN7kLIzc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423310888255361024290613.png%2FYJqlIMOF3zH_0xkHu4fb5xExTC-e0myyuQsjN7kLIzc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=87ba1446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423310893255233536512789.png/JbhUSerYW3yHUHpdVHSjqwmQCd5y68r9GaPwkxmj8JM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423310893255233536512789.png%2FJbhUSerYW3yHUHpdVHSjqwmQCd5y68r9GaPwkxmj8JM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=34c9c9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423310895792918528698207.png/c-EIK1QXQKm0-sqA8F46uXhQlLA71XQmH0licB9JYnA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423310895792918528698207.png%2Fc-EIK1QXQKm0-sqA8F46uXhQlLA71XQmH0licB9JYnA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1619a195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423310898083139584243506.png/uP2Z5QR5iA1mLa33m31V5GrihdUVVkcy0LOXJdCzlyU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423310898083139584243506.png%2FuP2Z5QR5iA1mLa33m31V5GrihdUVVkcy0LOXJdCzlyU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fa69f778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423311875669889024194738.png/mOpL6DpVsLkTOjFVfSs-XZlJbaYIzD4E-K__qviv_6o?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423311875669889024194738.png%2FmOpL6DpVsLkTOjFVfSs-XZlJbaYIzD4E-K__qviv_6o%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d8297615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423311872813436928718504.png/Q6yz7-j61JNhIhNxFasMDrVrPgBaCB0MmDJxGZgycRk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423311872813436928718504.png%2FQ6yz7-j61JNhIhNxFasMDrVrPgBaCB0MmDJxGZgycRk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=367ad717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423310883062550528041395.png/BrEXm_QIBCvDEQJQIeatXPNSjuT2sjra21bJLttWyS4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423310883062550528041395.png%2FBrEXm_QIBCvDEQJQIeatXPNSjuT2sjra21bJLttWyS4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=91050159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423310885809950720829046.png/-vmeIxqvZ3f4vO-8ZVb5FfqaSUEvjUbf8bwwn_G8MJ8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423310885809950720829046.png%2F-vmeIxqvZ3f4vO-8ZVb5FfqaSUEvjUbf8bwwn_G8MJ8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e7eff295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三名被捕男子25-27歲，其中包括達塞拉的男同事。警方向媒體公佈了另外9名在逃者的名字，達塞拉死前參加跨年派對中的每個人都被包括在內。菲律賓眾議員艾瑞克．葉（Eric Yap）懸賞10萬披索（約港幣1萬6千元），呼籲民眾提供在逃嫌犯線索，協助警方破案。<br />\n<br />\n馬尼拉《太陽星報》報道，菲律賓旅遊部（DOT）昨（5日）指四星級的城市花園大酒店其可能違反「ㄧ般社區隔離」(General Community Quarantine, GCQ)措施--馬尼拉以及其都會地區酒店不得提供休閒目的的住宿，勒令酒店管理層三天内解釋，爲何當天容許死者在内多人Staycation跨年派對。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：楊倩"},{"pid":"a12fbf32b8d61ada80beb3bee20aab135a3946fd","tid":2355972,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34f6ceeecf63ade597349a81e877249ec411144","tid":2355972,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"無其他女人？？？"},{"pid":"9f51999ad3d24c9146f53c309a6e2148c9d89e21","tid":2355972,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:49:55.000Z","msg":"嘩，咁混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0f4e5459dd95d870b0ad379980489695afbe38","tid":2355972,"uid":47328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T23:56:22.000Z","msg":"懸賞10萬披索<br />\n咁少有人會比料咩"},{"pid":"c0f59a616308bdeea8b1bc9d41bd78178b0bccbe","tid":2355972,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca0f4e5459dd95d870b0ad379980489695afbe38","tid":2355972,"uid":4732